{"tid":579471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[慶祝習帝登基之歌]  我們中華帝國將席卷全世界","createTime":"2018-03-03T15:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T19:50:38.000Z","uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f63744e3a8723e24d8ce9b87c4656e60951add46","tid":579471,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"我們中華帝國將席卷全世界<br />\n從高鐵上經過中亞再繞回東亞<br />\n屆時全球的人們將高歌<br />\n我們的領袖!習近平! 偉大的元首!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們中華帝國將席卷全世界<br />\n從一帶一路上經過中亞再繞回東亞<br />\n屆時全球的人們將高歌<br />\n我們的領袖!習近平! 偉大的元首!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各國將會認清自己的實力<br />\n當我們各方面都影響全世界之後<br />\n感謝的深深一鞠躬<br />\n這是來自全球最偉大的領袖向你的致敬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各國將會認清自己的實力<br />\n當我們各方面都影響全世界之後<br />\n感謝的深深一鞠躬<br />\n這是來自全球最偉大的元首向你的致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n習始帝萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43280892d62026c96fa961c55f3abd43fe83977","tid":579471,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"原本係邊首"},{"pid":"78ec62682136c3335aefbdb956b3825036294330","tid":579471,"uid":24140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b43280892d62026c96fa961c55f3abd43fe83977","tid":579471,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"原本係邊首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"20歲以上既應該知邊首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ef524ea294d1efdfb30da5b3e58f811062ad63","tid":579471,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"蘇聯??"},{"pid":"7a2c11e39d2eeee615415132c08615d82